{"tid":807560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航班100人不適　降落紐約強制隔離","createTime":"2018-09-05T15:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T12:07:42.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dfbdca40bd363eee954b17b24bb1bd6555c611cb","tid":807560,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"阿聯酋航空一架從杜拜起飛的E203航班驚傳集體感染！外媒報導，美國當地時間5日上午8時50班機抵達紐約，機上空服人員透露，約有100名乘客感到嚴重身體不適，伴隨咳嗽、發燒症狀，疑似集體感染疾病，目前該航班已被甘迺迪機場強制隔離。<br />\n據悉，該航班為A380客機，機上載有約500名乘客，已經降落甘迺迪機場、停靠4號航站緊急隔離。現場約有7輛救護車在跑道上等待救援，美國疾管局將對乘客及飛機進行檢查。目前乘客不適原因尚不名，初步判斷可能與飛機上的食物有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 快訊／杜拜航班爆「集體感染」！100人同時不適　降落紐約強制隔離 | ETtoday國際新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 手機版 | ETtoday MobileWeb <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180905/1252402.htm#ixzz5QEw51s9K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180905%2F1252402.htm%23ixzz5QEw51s9K&d=WCv99913tef268%2BYayrycL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b9ecfca2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180905/1252402.htm#ixzz5QEw51s9K</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"46cb1d2ae780f0021940bd768301330d45d2136b","tid":807560,"uid":81156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"生化襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67c19fc043bc870fb74ffee134247a2045317d7","tid":807560,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"邊條仆街體味咁撚濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ff54e002b48d3fecda22b0c5e416c3f08bad36","tid":807560,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"Quarantine <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f676d6